    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长施纳贝尔认为进一步降息的空间有限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/ecb-rate-cuts-schnabel-sees-only-limited-room-for-further-reductions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执委会委员伊莎贝尔·施纳贝尔表示，欧洲央行需要警惕过度降息，因为借贷成本已经接近不再抑制经济的水平，降息可能会适得其反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/ecb-rate-cuts-schnabel-sees-only-limited-room-for-further-reductions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 08:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众汽车出售新疆生产基地 退出争议地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/volkswagen-sells-xinjiang-sites-to-leave-controversial-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迫于投资者对中国西部地区可能存在侵犯人权行为的担忧，大众汽车集团 (Volkswagen AG) 将终止其在新疆的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/volkswagen-sells-xinjiang-sites-to-leave-controversial-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 08:03:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的政策选择和美国数据引发市场关注，股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们消化了唐纳德·特朗普的最新内阁任命，并期待一系列美国经济数据来寻找利率前景的线索，欧洲股市下跌，美国股指期货小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 22:52:07 GMT</pubDate>
